                             T U R B O M O L E   

                          a o f o r c e - program

                        using direct algorithms for

                       SCF level calculations of
                         * harmonic force constants
                         * hyperpolarizabilities
                         * IR and RAMAN intensities
                         * VCD intensities

                       DFT level calculations of
                         * harmonic force constants
                         * IR intensities
                                                   
